   Pattern: [32m(npm owner|password|htpasswd|auth_?token|secret_?key|private_?key|authorized_keys?|npmrc|\.ssh|usersecrets?|api_?keys|nuget\.config|\.identityservice)[0m
[30;1m2 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m3 | [0m[35mThis `jupyter_server_config.py` defines and enables a `SystemPasswordIdentityProvider`.[0m
[30;1m4 | [0m[35mThis IdentityProvider checks the entered password against your system password using PAM.[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35mOnly the current user's password (the user the server is running as) is accepted.[0m
